import React from 'react';
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom';
import Card from './Cards';
import './index.css';

ReactDOM.render(
  <>
    <Card
      imgsrc='https://i.pinimg.com/736x/bd/9b/e9/bd9be9cfc97ba73c66f51e927f2bfcc5.jpg'
      title="A Netflix Orignal Series"
      sname='Dark'
      link='https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80100172'
    />
    <Card
      imgsrc='https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTG-0Z7iHcswKk6UZwa5SH04u1RMjX4EuF-Sg&usqp=CAU'
      title="A Netflix Orignal Series"
      sname='Extra Curricular'
      link='https://www.netflix.com/in/title/80990668'

    />
    <Card
      imgsrc='https://cdn.europosters.eu/image/750/posters/stranger-things-one-sheet-season-2-i67844.jpg'
      title="A Netflix Orignal Series"
      sname='Stranger Things'
      link='https://www.netflix.com/in/title/81001209'
    />
  </>,
  document.getElementById("root")
);
